d 'CITYTOPROVINCE': module to standardize Chinese city names and generate corresponding provinces in Stata
d
d   This package provides functions to standardize Chinese city
d names and map them to their corresponding provinces, autonomous
d regions, municipalities, or special administrative regions in
d Stata. It handles both full city names and common variations,
d supporting more than 330 prefecture-level cities and above. The
d command facilitates data cleaning and regional analysis involving
d Chinese geographic information. 
d
d KW: data management
d KW: China
d
d Requires: Stata version 14
d
d Distribution-Date: 20250909
d
d Author:  Xiaokang Wu,  Nanjing University of Science and Technology
d Support: email   wuxk@@njust.edu.cn
d
f citytoprovince.ado
f citytoprovince.sthlp
